  "texts": [
    "Although the performance gap remains between LLaMA-2 and ChatGPT after distillation, LLaMA-2 trained with fine-grained rewards can close the gap or even outperform Chat-GPT.",
    "Training with a combined RS and RL leads to an average of 4.0%, 0.9%, 10.6% improvements over ChatGPT among all evaluation metrics on ASQA, QAMPARI, and ELI5 respectively.Fine-grained rewards are better than holistic rewards.",
    "We compare fine-grained rewards with holistic ones for model training.",
    "Table 1 shows the outstanding effectiveness of fine-grained rewards in all training setups (RS, RL, RS+RL).",
    "We observe higher performance gains with fine-grained rewards in almost all metrics and all datasets."
